*Averaged over colorscale & legend orientation
*FILES: 
*    Exp1_SPSS_outNoCSLeg-dMoreQuant.csv
*    Exp2_SPSS_outNoCSLeg-dMoreQuant.csv
*    Exp3_SPSS_outNoCSLeg-dMoreQuant.csv
*    Exp4_SPSS_outNoCSLeg-dMoreQuant.csv
*    Exp5_SPSS_outNoCSLeg-dMoreQuant.csv
*------------------------------------------------------------

*mixed design ANOVA: 2 conditions (congruent vs. incongruent) x 2 encoded mappings (dark-more quantity vs. light-more quantity).
GLM Dm Lm BY Condition
  /WSFACTOR=EncodedMapping 2 Polynomial
  /METHOD=SSTYPE(3)
  /PRINT=DESCRIPTIVE ETASQ PARAMETER
  /CRITERIA=ALPHA(.05)
  /WSDESIGN=EncodedMapping
  /DESIGN=Condition.



